flowchart TD
  A[Client requests limit and optional cursor] --> B[DTO validates limit cursor sort fields]
  B --> C[Service passes query to repository]
  C --> D[buildPrismaCursorQuery]
  D --> E[Query take limit plus one]
  E --> F[Optional cursor id and skip one]
  F --> G[Order by sort field and id tiebreaker]
  G --> H[(PostgreSQL indexed scan)]
  H --> I[Repository returns rows]
  I --> J[buildCursorPagination]
  J --> K{Rows greater than limit?}
  K -->|yes| L[Trim extra row set hasNext true nextCursor last returned id]
  K -->|no| M[hasNext false nextCursor null]
  L --> N[ApiResponseInterceptor moves meta to response]
  M --> N
  N --> O[Client requests next page with nextCursor]
